Convert HLD to LLD using 3 paradigm
UML diagram - Unified Modelling Language diagram
OOPS principals
SOLID principals

Design Patterns
-Factory Design Pattern
-Abstract factory Pattern
-Singleton Pattern
-Observer Pattern

UML diagram: Diagram consist of classes, interfaces, relations
Class diagram from Structured UML diagram.
Sequence, Use case and Activity from Behavioral UML diagram.

##### System Design #####
Systematic process involving phases
Planning, analysis, designing, deploying, and testing.

System Analysis: Process of collecting requirements(functional and non-functional) so as to prose out any business design logic.
long & simple process, lesser time
System Design: Process of portraying down business logic for new ones or updating the existing ones.
short & complex process, more time

