### Relational Dbms ### (Confused)

1. They are excellent at keeping data transactions secure.
2. They provide the ability to write complex SQL queries for data analysis and reporting.
3. Their models can ensure and enfore business rules at the data layer adding a level of data integrity not found in a non-relational database.